latestIgtvVideos.title: When your dream is bigger than your fears, everything is possible ♥️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Love is in the air #skydivedubai 
This was definitely one of the best experiences ever..
Suprisingly, I wasn’t scared at all before doing it until the moment the plane’s door opened and i could feel the intense wind and see how high we were, but after the jump, whatever fear  I had was gone! So why waste our time and energy worrying for no reason, right ? Go where you most feel alive 🤩♥️
